    "shortDescription": "<p>You create a spectral choir and conduct its tortured, ghostly moans, deluding listeners into believing they are suffering the torments of the dead.</p><p>The transparent singers occupy a 10-foot cube, but they are intangible and do not interfere with creatures in any physical way, nor can they be attacked.</p><p>Creatures within 30 feet of the choir experience wracking pain that causes them to take a -2 penalty on attack rolls, skill checks, and ability checks.</p><p>Individuals who exit the area of effect take these penalties for an additional 2 rounds before the delusion wears off.</p>",
